Palestinian Teenage Arrest A 15 year old Palestinian boy accused of throwing stones at the barrier in the West Bank, says the Israeli authorities mistreated him whilst he was detained. We hear from Defence for Children International that interrogations of Palestinian youngsters should be video-taped. Sailing Dreams The homeless men in Poland building a ship to sail round the world. Oscar Nomination And the South African actress, Leleti Khumalo tells of the impact of playing an HIV positive woman in the Oscar nominated film, "Yesterday". Show less